This paper deals with the impact of imperfect channel state information on the degrees of freedom of a broadcast channel, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT). The paper also discusses a novel transmission scheme, which could fall under the category of networked systems (cs.NI) or signal processing (cs.SI). The paper may also be relevant to multimedia systems (cs.MM) and communication and information theory (cs.CE).
